t your stay to be great. If there\'s anything we can do to improve our odds of achieving greatness, we hope you will let us know.\r\n\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Policies', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-21 09:03:05', '2018-06-21 09:03:05', '', 8, 'http://127.0.0.1:3020/uncategorized/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
