(65, 1, '2018-06-21 09:08:08', '2018-06-21 09:08:08', '<img class=\"size-full wp-image-41 aligncenter\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel_group.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"438\" />\r\n<div class=\"layoutgrid\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"six columns contentblock\">\r\n<h2>The Whole Enchilada</h2>\r\n<section>\r\n<h3>We Love Hosting Groups!</h3>\r\nThe size and design of our property offer an extremely memorable and laid-back experience. Guests have the freedom of a home-like <a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-meeting-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"225\" align=\"right\" /></a>environment, with the comfort and service of a luxury hotel. Best of all, our staff will serve as your group’s personal concierges, taking the worry and hassle off of you as the host!\r\n\r\nWhether you are planning a girlfriends’ getaway, a milestone birthday celebration, lodging for your wedding, or perhaps a company retreat, we’d love to create the perfect experience for your group. <a href=\"mailto:hey@heywoodhotel.com?subject=Group rentals? Tell me more!\">Email us</a> and tell us more!\r\n\r\n</section><!-- Meeting at Heywood content -->\r\n<h3>Meetings at the Heywood</h3>\r\n<section><section id=\"meetings_heywood\">You\'re not the average company, we\'re not your average hotel!\r\n\r\nWe offer creative space for corporate retreats and other \"coffee-table\" style meetings. With a full-property rental, we can accommodate meetings of 10-25 participants. Our meeting rates bundle lodging and are quite affordable. <a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-coffeetable-meeting.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" /></a>We include support staff, white boards, coffee, tea and water service, and catering assistance if needed. Our meeting space is full of natural light and perfect for team building. We’d love to inspire your team to unlock its greatest collective potential!\r\n\r\n</section><!-- Gatherings -->\r\n<h3>Parties, Events &amp; Private Gatherings</h3>\r\n<section id=\"gatherings\">Small events are welcome at the Heywood with rental of the full property. Please <a href=\"mailto:hey@heywoodhotel.com?subject=Group%20rentals?%20Tell%20me%20more!\">email us</a> with what you have in mind and we’ll take it from there!\r\n\r\n</section><!-- Activities Adventure -->\r\n<h3>Activities and Adventures</h3>\r\n<section id=\"actionadventure\">Combine your stay at the Heywood with an outdoor adventure, city tour, private dining or shopping experience, or visit to a craftsman studio where you can make your own souvenirs. Great for friends and corporate teams! We can help you arrange an activity that makes your stay in Austin truly one to remember.\r\n\r\n</section></section></div>\r\n<div class=\"six columns contentblock\"><!-- The Nitty Gritty -->\r\n<h2>The Nitty Gritty</h2>\r\n<section>\r\n<h3><a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-front.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"225\" align=\"right\" /></a>Group Size</h3>\r\nFull-property rentals for lodging can accommodate up to 15 guests. Standard group rentals for lodging can accommodate a maximum of 6 guests, to ensure the comfort of other guests staying with us. For private events, please inquire.\r\n<h3>Rooms &amp; Occupancy</h3>\r\nThe Heywood has 7 rooms. Each room has one king- or queen-sized luxury bed and can sleep a maximum of two guests. Room 7 has an additional sofa sleeper and can sleep a third guest. Each room has a private bath.<a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-roof-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"225\" align=\"right\" /></a>\r\n<h3>What’s Included</h3>\r\nWith a full property rental, your group will have exclusive use of our 7 guest rooms, plus lobby, outdoor courtyard and patio areas. Our concierge and housekeeping staff are on site daily from 7:00am to 7:00pm and are completely dedicated to your group’s needs. All rates include free parking, free wifi, free coffee/tea service, free concierge service and daily housekeeping, and VIP extras. We have free bikes that can be used by hotel guests during business hours and we can assist larger groups with renting additional bikes. There are no additional or hidden fees.\r\n<h3>Cancellation &amp; Change Policy</h3>\r\n<a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-roof-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"225\" align=\"right\" /></a>\r\n\r\nYour rental agreement will contain the full policies for your group reservation including the cancellation and change policy. For full-property rentals, 50% is typically required to reserve the property and the balance is due at the time your cancellation window closes (typically 60 or 90 days prior to arrival). Discounts are provided for payment by check or wire transfer.\r\n\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Group Rentals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-21 09:08:08', '2018-06-21 09:08:08', '', 38, 'http://127.0.0.1:3020/uncategorized/38-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
