oup will have exclusive use of our 7 guest rooms, plus lobby, outdoor courtyard and patio areas. Our concierge and housekeeping staff are on site daily from 7:00am to 7:00pm and are completely dedicated to your group’s needs. All rates include free parking, free wifi, free coffee/tea service, free concierge service and daily housekeeping, and VIP extras. We have free bikes that can be used by hotel guests during business hours and we can assist larger groups with renting additional bikes. There are no additional or hidden fees.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Cancellation &amp; Change Policy</h3>\r\n<a class=\"badge\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/heywoodhotel-roof-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"225\" align=\"right\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"textblock\">Your rental agreement will contain the full policies for your group reservation including the cancellation and change policy. For full-property rentals, 50% is typically required to reserve the property and the balance is due at the time your cancellation window closes (typically 60 or 90 days prior to arrival). Discounts are provided for payment by check or wire transfer.</p>\r\n\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"slideshow-container\">\r\n<h2>Guest Quotes</h2>\r\n[slide-anything id=\'67\']\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Group Rentals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-21 09:28:42', '2018-06-21 09:28:42', '', 38, 'http://127.0.0.1:3020/uncategorized/38-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
