(165, 1, '2018-06-21 14:31:05', '2018-06-21 14:31:05', '<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/googlemap.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"439\" />\r\n<div class=\"layoutgrid\">\r\n<div class=\"row copy\">\r\n<div class=\"eight columns\">\r\n<h1>No car needed to see the best of Austin.</h1>\r\n<p>The Heywood Hotel is located just blocks from downtown, the Convention Center, Rainey Street, Lady Bird Lake, Sixth Street and more -- walkable or $5 by taxi or rideshare. We\'re right on the #17 busline, and we offer free bikes to tool around town. We\'re smack dab in the middle of the hip East Austin neighborhood where you’ll find some of the city’s best restaurants and cocktails, eclectic art, and best breakfast tacos in the universe. Free parking is provided for guests with cars. See <a class=\"white\" href=\"/features\">Features.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns addressblock\">\r\n<h2>Location</h2>\r\n<address>1609 East Cesar Chavez Street<br>\r\nAustin, Texas 78702<br>\r\n2 stoplights east of I-35<br>\r\nBetween Comal &amp; Chalmers</address><a title=\"Phone Number\" href=\"tel:+15122715522\">(512) 271-5522</a><br>\r\n<a title=\"Email Us\" href=\"mailto:hay@heywoodhotel.om\">hey@heywoodhotel.com</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"eight columns attractions\">\r\n<h2>Distance to popular Austin attractions:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"splitcolumns\">\r\n<div class=\"halfcolumn\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Under 1 mile:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\n 	<li>More than 30 top restaurants and bars including:\r\n<a href=\"http://www.launderetteaustin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Launderette</a>, <a href=\"http://www.bufalinapizza.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bufalina</a>, <a href=\"http://kemuri-tatsuya.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kemuri Tatsu-ya</a>, <a href=\"http://www.veracruzallnatural.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Veracruz All Natural</a>, <a href=\"https://www.labarbecue.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">La Barbecue</a>, <a href=\"http://via313.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Via 313 Pizzeria</a>, <a href=\"http://www.thewhitehorseaustin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The White Horse</a>, <a href=\"http://www.weatherupnyc.com/austin-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Weather Up</a>, <a href=\"https://www.scootinnaustin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Scoot Inn</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.austinconventioncenter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Austin Convention Center</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Lady Bird Lake / Town Lake</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.austintexas.org/things-to-do/entertainment-districts/rainey-street/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rainey Street District (bars and restaurants)</a></li>\r\n 	<li>French Legation</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.cemetery.state.tx.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Texas State Cemetery</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Festival Beach Park</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>1 mile:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://franklinbarbecue.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Franklin Barbecue</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Downtown Austin</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.batcon.org/index.php/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/cab-intro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Congress Avenue Bat Bridge</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://6street.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Sixth Street Entertainment District</a> (bars and nightlife)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.austintexas.org/things-to-do/entertainment-districts/red-river/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Red River District</a> (live music)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.2ndstreetdistrict.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Second Street</a> (shopping)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"halfcolumn\">\r\n\r\n<strong>A littler farther:</strong>\r\n<ul clas